===================================
Production Dockerfile
==================================


FROM node:20-alpine

WORKDIR /app

COPY package*.json ./#npm init -y = package.json, and npm install express = package-lock.json & node_modules auto create 

RUN npm ci --omit=dev #npm ci = install depedencies clean and fast , --omit=dev = Dont install Development dependencies 
COPY . .

EXPOSE 3000

CMD ["npm", "start"]




Why node:20-alpine?
Smaller image
Faster download
Lower storage usage
Reduced attack surface
